{
  "stem": "4189.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this wall went all the way through Holland, all the way through Belgium, and to France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where we were sent, we were sent to build that section by Boulogne, Calais.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to build a road so that they could bring trucks with supplies up to the beaches.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to, we had to carry water and cement all day long, back and forth, so that they could build these fortifications.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because the sanitary conditions were so bad, I myself and some others, we were five of us, we contracted typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the, the guards that were guarding us, they got scared because they were afraid that if we had typhoid fever, we would spread the disease to them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they took us out and they brought us into Boulogne, into the city of Boulogne, into a regular civilian hospital where in the basement, they put up a room, they put us up in a room there with beds.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were, for the first time in many weeks, we were sleeping in clean beds with, with nice white sheets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these French doctors from the hospital, they nursed us back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were in the hospital for about, I would say, maybe three weeks till we got better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then one day those guards showed up again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said to us, we have to go back, they're evacuating the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They're sending everybody back to Brussels, to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we could hardly believe them because, you know, after we saw all these things that went on there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when we got back to the camp, we saw that the camp was broken up and everybody was ready to march and go on trucks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they brought us to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
